a psychological problem.

00:23:14.695 --> 00:23:18.510 align:middle line:90%


00:23:18.510 --> 00:23:21.780 align:middle line:84%
In December of 1948,
just as Project Sign

00:23:21.780 --> 00:23:24.870 align:middle line:84%
