00:24:06.000 --> 00:24:07.830 align:middle line:84%
only to see
sightings immediately

00:24:07.830 --> 00:24:09.250 align:middle line:90%
hit an all-time high.

00:24:09.250 --> 00:24:12.520 align:middle line:90%


00:24:12.520 --> 00:24:15.220 align:middle line:84%
