00:26:01.790 --> 00:26:04.010 align:middle line:84%
that flying saucers
were coming to Earth,

00:26:04.010 --> 00:26:06.920 align:middle line:84%
and they'd started watching us
intensely because they began

00:26:06.920 --> 00:26:08.540 align:middle line:90%
monitoring our atomic bombs.

00:26:08.540 --> 00:26:12.300 align:middle line:90%


00:26:12.300 --> 00:26:15.910 align:middle line:84%
>> In 1950, men throughout
the world learned to look

00:26:15.910 --> 00:26:17.980 align:middle line:90%
on the brutal face of communism.

00:26:17.980 --> 00:26:21.820 align:middle line:90%
Berlin, powder keg--

00:26:21.820 --> 00:26:24.960 align:middle line:84%
>> As the road to the Korean
