noticed a strange object

00:26:32.170 --> 00:26:34.180 align:middle line:90%
in the sky.

00:26:34.180 --> 00:26:36.640 align:middle line:84%
The pictures that Paul
Trent and his wife took

00:26:36.640 --> 00:26:41.020 align:middle line:84%
