analyzed UFO photos ever taken.

00:26:41.020 --> 00:26:42.760 align:middle line:84%
And while there have
been many attempts

00:26:42.760 --> 00:26:45.430 align:middle line:84%
to expose them as
faked, the efforts

00:26:45.430 --> 00:26:47.840 align:middle line:90%
have been far from convincing.

00:26:47.840 --> 00:26:51.590 align:middle line:84%
And there was also the lifelong
character of the Trents.

00:26:51.590 --> 00:26:54.490 align:middle line:84%
>> Everybody says,
straightforward, honest.

00:26:54.490 --> 00:26:58.360 align:middle line:84%
