00:30:23.940 --> 00:30:26.730 align:middle line:84%
But Smith's memo would
become of huge importance

00:30:26.730 --> 00:30:29.730 align:middle line:84%
when it came to light
in the late '70s.

00:30:29.730 --> 00:30:32.280 align:middle line:84%
It appeared to confirm
the existence of a crash

00:30:32.280 --> 00:30:35.940 align:middle line:84%
