above top secret control

00:30:35.940 --> 00:30:38.670 align:middle line:84%
group, ideas that
would loom large

00:30:38.670 --> 00:30:41.815 align:middle line:84%
in the UFO landscape of
the '80s and the '90s.

00:30:41.815 --> 00:30:46.920 align:middle line:90%


00:30:46.920 --> 00:30:50.280 align:middle line:84%
1951 would be a slow
