change it, personalize it--

01:31:27.570 --> 01:31:33.210 align:middle line:84%
in some way, make a new creation
out of the old materials.

01:31:33.210 --> 01:31:35.860 align:middle line:84%
We don't see that with
the abduction stories.

01:31:35.860 --> 01:31:37.830 align:middle line:84%
There'll be some degree
of personalization.

01:31:37.830 --> 01:31:41.340 align:middle line:84%
But as far as the actual
phenomenology of the story,

01:31:41.340 --> 01:31:44.850 align:middle line:84%
there's really surprisingly
little variation.

01:31:44.850 --> 01:31:48.000 align:middle line:84%
We get all kinds of variation
with the urban legends,

01:31:48.000 --> 01:31:50.410 align:middle line:84%
but we don't get them
with the abduction story.

01:31:50.410 --> 01:31:54.420 align:middle line:84%
Now, the second problem
is that these stories

01:31:54.420 --> 01:31:55.740 align:middle line:90%
